tests.prompt:
Draft a save plan for a client with 78% churn probability. Return JSON:
{
  "proposed_actions": [
    {"action_type": "email" | "meeting" | "call" | "internal", "title": "...", "draft_content": "...", "owner": "...", "requires_approval": true}
  ],
  "talking_points": ["..."],
  "human_approval_required": true
}

Client: BlueOrbit Labs. Driver: missed deliverable (Q2 campaign launch slipped 2 weeks) + angry email from marketing director. Contract renews in 45 days.

CRITICAL: Every item in proposed_actions MUST have requires_approval: true. The top-level human_approval_required MUST be true. No action should be described as if it has already been taken.
